'''十月妈咪'''（'''O.C.T. Mami'''）是一个中国孕妇装公司，总部住在[[上海市|上海市]][[普陀区_(上海市)|普陀区]]。<ref>"[http://www.octmami.com/about_us.php?page=8 联系我们] {{Wayback|url=http://www.octmami.com/about_us.php?page=8 |date=20150325000540 }}." 十月妈咪. Retrieved on May 20, 2015. "地址：上海市普陀区金沙江路1340弄172支弄A区16号楼2-3楼 （新曹杨高新技术工业园 ）"</ref> 2014年十月妈咪是最大的中国孕妇装公司。<ref name=ChanZakhourp164>Chan, Savio (陳少宏)<!-- http://www.worldjournal.com/2174140/article-%E9%99%B3%E5%B0%91%E5%AE%8F-18%E6%97%A5%E8%AB%87%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E8%B6%85%E7%B4%9A%E6%B6%88%E8%B2%BB%E8%80%85/?ref=%E4%BC%91%E5%A3%AB%E9%A0%93/%E9%81%94%E6%8B%89%E6%96%AF - http://www.webcitation.org/6YoBp6L9u -->与Michael Zakkour. ''{{link-en|China's Super Consumers: What 1 Billion Customers Want and How to Sell it to Them|China's Super Consumers}}'' (中國超級消費者). [[John_Wiley_&_Sons|John Wiley & Sons]], 2014. Online: p. [https://books.google.com/books?id=13LvBQAAQBAJ&pg=PA164 164] {{Wayback|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=13LvBQAAQBAJ&pg=PA164 |date=20160423022125 }}. ISBN 1118834747, 9781118834749. -- print: ISBN 978-1-118-83474-9 p. 164. (Subsection "Baby Boom", in Chapter 18: Marketing)</ref>

1997年赵浦与涂文虹，赵浦的妻子，创建十月妈咪。<ref name=ChanZakhourp164/><ref name=ForbesYang>杨维维. "[http://3g.forbeschina.com/review/201208/0019601.shtml 赵浦：十月妈咪初长成] {{WebCite|url=https://www.webcitation.org/6YoqmpbZQ?url=http://3g.forbeschina.com/review/201208/0019601.shtml |date=20150526181142 |dateformat=iso }}" (). 《[[福布斯|福布斯]]中国》. 2012年8月28日. Retrieved on May 27, 2015.</ref>

2007年，[[徐熙娣|徐熙娣]]拥护十月妈咪。<ref>Li, Shanyou, S Ramakrishna Velamuri, Dong Liang and Xu Leiping. "[http://businesstoday.intoday.in/story/oct-mami-faces-challenge-to-balance-online-and-offline-sales/1/217144.html Balancing online and offline] {{WebCite|url=https://www.webcitation.org/6Yehs3A7p?url=http://businesstoday.intoday.in/story/oct-mami-faces-challenge-to-balance-online-and-offline-sales/1/217144.html |date=20150520020851 |dateformat=iso }}" (). {{link-en|Business Today (business magazine)|Business Today}} (Indian business magazine). April 12, 2015. Retrieved on May 20, 2015.</ref>

2014年，弗若斯特沙利文公司发布报告，以零售额计，市场份额排名前五的企业依次是十月妈咪、[[婧麒|婧麒]]、[[快乐屋|快乐屋]]、孕之彩和添香，这五家企业总共占有了中国孕妇装市场6.1%的市场份额。<ref>{{cite news |title=弗若斯特沙利文公司发表中国孕产用品市场研究报告 - 中国日报网 |url=https://caijing.chinadaily.com.cn/2016-09/14/content_26798965.htm |accessdate=2021-11-04 |work=中国日报网 |archive-date=2021-11-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211104063935/https://caijing.chinadaily.com.cn/2016-09/14/content_26798965.htm }}</ref>

